## ğŸ¤“ Understanding the Prompts

When in interactive mode, youâ€™ll notice:

- **`>>>`** â†’ Primary prompt (ready for a new statement).
    
- **`...`** â†’ Continuation prompt (waiting for you to finish something).
    

Example:

```
>>> if True: 
>>> ... print("Hi there!") 
>>> ... Hi there!
>>> 
```

